org.apache.ignite.tools.javadoc

Class IgniteLinkTaglet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.tools.javadoc.IgniteLinkTaglet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.sun.tools.doclets.Taglet

    public class IgniteLinkTaglet
extends Object
implements com.sun.tools.doclets.Taglet
    Represents Class tag. This tag can be used as replacement of Class tag that references to the Ignite class that is not in classpath. Class and its arguments should have fully qualified names.
